  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Hey guys! this is a message from Fin. The game is still in very early
    development as we've still only been working on it for about 2 months. We did
    want the release to be the full game however due to us not being able to work
    on this full time and only in our spare time we weren't able to meet that.\n\nWe
    can promise however that sometime in the future there will be updates made as
    we slowly progress into a full fledged release!\n\nHowever, as you read this
    now just know we are taking a little break from development as this passion project
    has kind of taken over our lives over the last two months.  \n\nBut, just know
    \"I'll always come back\".\n\n- Naughty Corner Games"
